msgstr "Pronašli ste nedostajući prijevod?"

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:93
msgid ""
"This link will create a new GitHub issue pre-filled with a language code."
msgstr ""
"Ova poveznica će stvoriti novi GitHub problem s unaprijed ispunjenim "
