"This script will prompt you to enter a new password for the admin user. You "
"must run it from the host system where the Grylli container is running."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj skript će vas tražiti da unesete novu lozinku za administrativnog "
"korisnika. Morate ga pokrenuti s host sustava na kojem se pokreće Grylli "
